data.description: Excellent Opportunity to own Triplex in the heart of Los Angeles, Unit 1 Front consist 1 bed 1 bath, 2nd Unit is 1 bed 1 bath and third Unit is 2 bed  1 bath, Property features 3 detached 1 car garages, and Plenty of space for parking. Centrally located near freeways, school and shopping centers. New Roof, Exterior Paint, Second Unit has new Tile in entire house. New Plumbing in unit 345, and 345 1/2 Unit 347 new electricity and new shower installed.
